{"tid":2335720,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–塑膠垃圾對駱駝的禍害","createTime":"2020-12-22T05:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T12:26:31.000Z","uid":38861,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"75eedfb28e2d4b0daa56270852832bc460a354a9","tid":2335720,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"塑膠影響海洋生物的新聞屢見不鮮，但對陸地生物的影響也絕對不能忽視。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0sGk1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0sGk1M.jpg&h=1bf3201c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）全球約有三千五百萬隻駱駝，而阿拉伯聯合酋長國(阿聯酋)至少有三十九萬隻駱駝聚居。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8YaYOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8YaYOu.png&h=88f81ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自2008年起，三萬隻駱駝的死亡個案中，就有三百宗個案相信是因為吞食塑膠廢物引致而死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）圖中為五份在駱駝身內找到的塑膠廢物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuRTb8x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuRTb8x.png&h=0b398036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塑膠廢物的化學物不但會影響駱駝健康，更會阻礙器官正常運作，甚至乎給予牠們錯誤的飽肚感，使牠們停止進食飢餓而死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=d8ff6a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0140196320302731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0140196320302731&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=66635bb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0140196320302731</a>"},{"pid":"b161e91923f9115a2445d12c9e4e88f6ca19bc9b","tid":2335720,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"咁多文咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bacaaa87577f6614236d2e97514b43ecbe97581","tid":2335720,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5502646d529c7124c2be815ee94ea321fdf8b4e","tid":2335720,"uid":342854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"好慘 原本已經要俾人騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3720a54737b9b4f86a048ddf06b63e1ba36ad5a3","tid":2335720,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aafb1d6e425b0d57625b8d09e291201009acf2","tid":2335720,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5502646d529c7124c2be815ee94ea321fdf8b4e","tid":2335720,"uid":342854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"好慘 原本已經要俾人騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"成日見外國大肥婆騎佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f6f7b8916a52b5a43bf2fb1ad761619a5e1624","tid":2335720,"uid":60120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0sGk1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0sGk1M.jpg&h=1bf3201c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm