gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f990604a6461a2c31a632f9fc18d86486e05dda1","tid":2335720,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"原來個沙漠咁鳩多垃圾架？"},{"pid":"aba4dec1d0ba22b78d4a65fc56e97da46b63ecc6","tid":2335720,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"我認知的沙漠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wowlavie-aws.hmgcdn.com/file/article_all/source/A1497794205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwowlavie-aws.hmgcdn.com%2Ffile%2Farticle_all%2Fsource%2FA1497794205.jpg&h=711e838d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"525a2ecf2334a9ceb4a6a75a6ef3e183991a25a2","tid":2335720,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f990604a6461a2c31a632f9fc18d86486e05dda1","tid":2335720,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"原來個沙漠咁鳩多垃圾架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"睇相就好似係，未去過唔知。<br />\n<br />\n文入面話沙漠地區大風同埋空礦，啲塑膠好容易從開蓋垃圾筒或者堆填區飛往沙漠各地，但係真唔係就真心唔清楚。"},{"pid":"fd37bb33b2fa9c8bca50772c65e67799731d708b","tid":2335720,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"樓主好多文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b816c496f4ec7d61197413db539b0e99b954a65","tid":2335720,"uid":155238,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:09:05.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得所有呢啲膠袋膠飲管膠樽食死啲生物嘅問題嘅原因從來都唔係因為呢啲嘢嘅出現，而係垃圾處理嘅問題，理得你幾多膠袋飲管，你好地地掉落垃圾桶去堆填區根本就唔會漂落個海到，個問題最多都只係啲膠喺堆填區到難分解同對土壤有污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d483e820387fb8044261033ad5ee4c6f649e75b","tid":2335720,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b816c496f4ec7d61197413db539b0e99b95